tools.description:
You must invoke the "Project_Request_Tool" attached using the following payload format:
    ```json
		  {
			"data": {
				"intake_type": "<intake_type>",
				 "generalRequestType": {
				 "name": "Supplier Offboarding",
				 "code": "7"
			},
				 "project_description": "<generate_description_based_on_conversation>", Example :Offboarding Microsoft (GEP-000010757) due to <reason>
				"suppliers": [
					{
						"sourceIdentificationNumber": "<sourceIdentificationNo>"
					}
				],
				"offboardedSupplierName": "<Supplier Name Being Offboarded>",
				"supplierOffboardReason": {
					"name": "<offboarding reason label or name>",
					"code": "<offboarding reason value or code>"
				},
				"is_supplier_offboarding_discussed_with_stakeholders": "<yes_no>",
                "offboardedSupplierName":"<supplier_name>",
                "attachmentObjList": "<attachments or uploaded files list>"  
			},
			"event": "<event_type>",
			"additionalData": {}
		}
     ```
